St._Paul.Lilydale, Minnesota:
Lilydale is a city in Dakota County, Minnesota, United States. The population was 623 at the 2010 census.


== Geography ==
According to the United States Census Bureau, the city has a total area of 0.87 square miles (2.25 km2), of which 0.58 square miles (1.50 km2) is land and 0.29 square miles (0.75 km2) is water.
